830
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:30,756
Papá que me estas dando tanto..

831
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:31,716
Escúchame.

832
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:34,956
Este dinero, se lo doy a ustedes dos hermanos para pagar la colegiatura.

833
00:34:34,980 --> 00:34:36,636
¿Comprender?

834
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:38,260
Ve rápido.

835
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:45,556
Zhong Fu.

836
00:34:45,580 --> 00:34:47,620
Ya lo diste.

837
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:53,236
Mengzou.

838
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,716
Tu dices, justo ahora

839
00:34:54,740 --> 00:34:57,036
